o </div><div class="t m19f4 x6 h28 y3d1 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">everyone may be able, through his own experience, to &apos;set his </div><div class="t m8ed x11 h28 y1321 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">seal to this, that God is true.&apos; John 3:33, A.R.V. He can bear witness to that </div><div class="t ma4d x11 h28 y1976 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">which he himself has seen and heard and felt of the power of Christ. He can </div><div class="t m1ac2 x11 h28 y7b0 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">testify: </div><div class="t m1142 x14 h28 y1d5 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot; &apos;I needed help, and I found it in Jesus. Every want was supplied, the </div><div class="t m1a0d x11 h28 y797 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hunger of my soul was satisfied; the Bible is to me the revelation of Christ. </div><div class="t ma4d x11 h28 y1012 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I believe in Jesus because He is to me a divine Saviour.&apos; </div><div class="t m2813 x95 h2c y1012 ff6 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;—Testimonies, </div><div class="t m21ac xca h28 y1012 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">vol. </div><div class="t m1ca4 x11 h28 y166b ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8, p. 321. </div><div class="t m2819 x5d h28 y824 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;We can bear witness to what we have known of the grace of Christ. This </div><div class="t m2e3 x11 h28 y76d ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is the witness for which our Lord calls, and for want of which the world is </div><div class="t ma85 x11 h28 ybf0 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">perishing.&quot;—The </div><div class="t me03 x2c h2c yaae ff6 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Desire of Ages, </div><div class="t m2353 x97 h28 yaae ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Page 340. </div><div class="t m13e x5d h28 yc3e ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t mcfb x36 h28 y1305 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">By what figure does the psalmist show the Lord&apos;s care for us? </div><div class="t ma96 x11 h28 y67 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ps. 23:1. See </div><div class="t m56d x6 h2c y67 ff6 fs14 fc0 sc0 